        &lt;p&gt;You can find our assets in this &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/free-the-people/assets&quot; target=&quot;github&quot;&gt;GitHub repository&lt;/a&gt;. These assets were previously licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution Share Alike 4.0 International license, but this week, we removed the license restrictions. Our intention all along was to make these images available to the public to use how they like, so the license was not necessary.&lt;/p&gt;
